<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فتاوى اللجنة الدائمة <span class="c2">(٨/٢٨٤-٢٨٦)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>